systems you're familiar with like running
times.

35
00:02:10,530 --> 00:02:13,970
Many disciplines use memorable sentences.

36
00:02:13,970 --> 00:02:17,780
The memory palace technique, placing
memorable images in a

37
00:02:17,780 --> 00:02:21,580
scene that's familiar to you, allows you
to dip into

38
00:02:21,580 --> 00:02:24,960
the strength of your visual memory system,
